text: Salako is a hat worn in French Antilles. Salako or Selako may also refer to * Salako language, a dialect of Kendayan language spoken in Borneo * Selako people, an ethnic of the Dayak people group from Borneo *Andy Salako (born 1972), Nigerian football defender *John Salako (born 1969), English footballer and sports television personality, brother of Andy *Lateef Akinola Salako (1935–2017), Nigerian academic
title: Salako (disambiguation)
